ype="withinCollection" target="L01183">Schnitzler an Bahr, 26. 10. 1901</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01185">Schnitzler an Bahr, 28. 10. 1901</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01183">Schnitzler an Bahr, 26. 10. 1901</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01185">Schnitzler an Bahr, 28. 10. 1901</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
